{"tid":1540403,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"太子站極大機會有手足被打死 唔好比林奠轉移視線","createTime":"2019-09-04T11:25:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T14:59:41.000Z","uid":34047,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"0442f8364625eb1d763c1f4f86c34022325ddba0","tid":1540403,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:25:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>-有一個人失蹤<br />\n-有機會有一個人死左 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">比警察打左半個鐘 嘔白泡 差佬見佢冇反應</span></span></span> 之後冇打 二三十分鐘後<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">由消防員 非救護人員 送走 完全冇反應</span></span><br />\n-差佬同佢地講強姦佢地係正常<br />\n-有被捕人士係警署被非禮 (摸胸)<br />\n-係警署去廁所時不能關門 而當時有其他性別既警員在場<br />\n-有日本人被捕 警方拒絕比佢聯繫大使館<br />\n-目擊者話傷者係送去瑪嘉烈唔係廣華<br />\n-速龍落電梯 踩住市民背部甚至頭部落<br />\n-去晒葵涌警署有70人（當中有啲係港島拘捕）<br />\n-凌晨時分有部分被拘捕人士送上全黑車往新屋嶺<br />\n-被捕人士名單有備注（例如：知名社工）<br />\n<br />\nSource:【831 太子站目擊者立法會見記者】</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n隔離post巴打整好<br />\n<br />\n而家講緊極大機會有人死有人失蹤<br />\n一定要繼續跟進呀"},{"pid":"9c25144a3599a68a66214db247ef02f96e0a851d","tid":1540403,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:26:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a0d7aae68f80d15040fdb193540777fd0fa0b7fc","tid":1540403,"uid":193032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:28:07.000Z","msg":"應該有人死"},{"pid":"6e51a3e41e7c2b070103e9f80d5683cbb0f8c9b2","tid":1540403,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:29:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">林鄭宣布撤回送中條例的六大陰謀</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1539227\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1539227</a><br />\n快啲同我入黎睇曬佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1923bebdcc35c5fdc5e503dd7f2718c1c6d4eed","tid":1540403,"uid":120431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:30:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vamod6p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVamod6p.jpg&h=05b4b4f2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RGvwnZM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRGvwnZM.png&h=a81c6f76&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c2b07f2f77219d6c1535ed1953c88aeb2ea2575c","tid":1540403,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0d7aae68f80d15040fdb193540777fd0fa0b7fc","tid":1540403,"uid":193032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:28:07.000Z","msg":"應該有人死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:33:46.000Z","msg":"好唔想但睇政府反應<br />\n連同埋之前封站<br />\n真係極有可能"},{"pid":"e38a0b83d96384a67db659ea3f0bda1a8a829afc","tid":1540403,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1923bebdcc35c5fdc5e503dd7f2718c1c6d4eed","tid":1540403,"uid":120431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:30:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vamod6p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVamod6p.jpg&h=05b4b4f2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RGvwnZM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRGvwnZM.png&h=a81c6f76&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:34:01.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家"},{"pid":"1eeac720aae50d38f437334a1619d924966cbcd4","tid":1540403,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:34:35.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n失蹤都好大件事啦"},{"pid":"0b547cac93d8d94b6f7eaeadecc60d780b98c097","tid":1540403,"uid":72800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:34:58.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港共殺人政權企圖以<strong>錄音、撤回、學季開始</strong><br />\n轉移<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">太子地鐵傷亡、<br />\n六警壓脊椎休克 <span style=\"color: teal;\">至今嚴重昏迷</span>、<br />\n新屋嶺、民主人權法案、<br />\n臥底實彈、武警滲透、<span style=\"color: green;\">清朝債主權問題</span><br />\n</span></strong></span>連串<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>核彈</strong></span><span style=\"color: red;\">事件焦點<br />\n醒呀大家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">政府帶緊風向</span><br />\n背後繼續大清算 入獄 利刑 一年後被失蹤</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">林鄭錄音：事件現時已經上升至「國家主權及國家安全的層次，\n加上世界兩大經濟體前所未有的張力」，她可以做的已經非常少。</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><blockquote><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">英、美領事館請願 大遊行</span></span></strong><br />\n審視中英聯合聲明 法定性<br />\n中共正統性<br />\n中共毀約 無視國際社會<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">請求國際介入香港前途</span></span></strong> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">施壓制裁港府 還港人雙普選 <br />\n協助制定民主進程</span></span></strong><br />\n香港人道災難 高壓滅聲 白色恐怖 <br />\n執法機器無法無天 受命中共 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">港府管治班子失去自治權 聽命中央</span><br />\n實彈恐怖 威嚇扼殺<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">民主自由</span>現代普世價值<br />\n<strong>人權民主法案 事在必行</strong></blockquote></div><br />\n<br />\n#1down4togo<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">暗黑兵法劇本 出沒注意：\n\n沒收gear 未來兩星期大量武警喬裝示威者 嫁禍衝擊\n內部分化示威者、\n酷刑凌虐威嚇被捕人士、\n邊緣打壓香港 渲染港獨 阻抗爭之風蔓延內陸、\n假新聞、擺拍、編輯、洗腦文宣製造風向 污名化運動、\n暴力鎮壓 拘捕 扣留 私刑 企圖瓦解前線、\n文宣 抹黑 嫁禍 插贜 示威者、\n暗殺 第一滴血 企圖逆轉民意 國際譴責、\n市民絕望噤聲 憤怒冷卻、\n中立派 賺錢派 政治疲勞、\n鼓吹經濟下滑風向 富豪商家屈服 加速瓦解、\n學季始開，拖延 分散 擊破、\n白色恐怖、清除異己、染紅香港\n\n拖字訣 雨傘結局 ⋯</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>這不只是反修例活動<br />\n這是屬於香港人的<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">時代革命</span></strong></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">流水革命</span></strong></div>"},{"pid":"2d852d5a274fe262d8cc5eced6c040005d3512a8","tid":1540403,"uid":74155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:36:19.000Z","msg":"香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！<br />\n香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！<br />\n香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！<br />\n香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！<br />\n香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！<br />\n香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！<br />\n香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！<br />\n香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！<br />\n香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！<br />\n香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！<br />\n香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！<br />\n香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！<br />\n香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！<br />\n香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！<br />\n香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！<br />\n香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！<br />\n香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！<br />\n香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！<br />\n香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！<br />\n香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！<br />\n香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！<br />\n香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！<br />\n香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！<br />\n香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！<br />\n香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！<br />\n香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！<br />\n香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！<br />\n香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！<br />\n香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！<br />\n香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！<br />\n香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！<br />\n香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！"},{"pid":"5ea1b0135303cf294f203e84cad615e58f07f391","tid":1540403,"uid":194069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:36:52.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96019ae1966ff57b6d87dc98d242661f9e75ae8e","tid":1540403,"uid":302831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:36:53.000Z","msg":"全面抵制藍色餐廳<br />\n一齊打經濟戰<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=10SCYSkgC9KMC_kAGtLChlGRLWVbk8NTs&amp;shorturl=1&amp;ll=22.289809900000016%2C114.1965917&amp;z=17\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fmaps%2Fd%2Fviewer%3Fmid%3D10SCYSkgC9KMC_kAGtLChlGRLWVbk8NTs%26shorturl%3D1%26ll%3D22.289809900000016%252C114.1965917%26z%3D17&d=HFtALxS4LzZA